cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper is about software engineering and machine learning, specifically deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper proposes a novel deep learning architecture for effort estimation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with open source projects, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.SD (Software Development).
